<ul>
<li><em>Windows Embedded media player now has seperate play functions for videos and playlists</em>, allowing easier addition of videos.</li>
<li>RCT2 Desktop redirect now changes the current video in the Embedded media player to Merry-Go-Round music. <em>(More of these to come)</em></li>
<li><strong>Added progression bar to state the current video time.</strong></li>
<li><strong>Added fast forward and rewind button functionality</strong> based on 10 second intervals which will later be adjustable.</li>
<li>The address bar including the HTML link of videos is now shorted by not including the current playlist inside the URL.</li>
<li><strong>Added a shuffle feature</strong> which will be applied to the current playlist when activated and reset back to the disabled state when selecting other videos. Enabling shuffle will visually change the state of the shuffle button alongside stating in the media player state, held in the footer.</li>
<li>Swapped out jank media player states in the footer and tied it closer to the Youtube API.</li>
<li><em>Media handling optimisation.</em></li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
